0.7.0:

* Update MemoryBackend, RedisBackend.
* Add ability to set SUPPORTS_VISIBILITY and SUPPORTS_INHERITANCE backend
  properties.
* Add LDAP Backend.
* Add our own in-memory cache in settings that we can use as secure cache.
* Remove SECURE_CACHE setting.
* Document DATA_BACKEND setting, update backend documentation.
* GroupNotFound/GroupExist should require two params: name and service.

Future:

* add support for /users/<user>/blobs
